Class EmployeeService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khalsa_ji.ems.service.EmployeeService

  • @Service
public class EmployeeService
extends java.lang.Object
    The class EmployeeService is a service class that provides a layer of abstraction over the functionality provided by the EmployeeRepository interface.

      • fire

        public void fire(Employee employee)
        Method to fire(delete) an instance of the Employee class specified by its id, without updating the manager id of its subordinates. It is used in the case of replacing an existing instance of the Employee class with an another instance of the same.
